<Content>very clean and friendly hotel I booked this hotel through an internet site for German hotels and wasn't dissappointed.The cost of the hotel was the same as others in the area but this one included breakfast. It was situated right in the middle of all the exclusive and designer shops on the Kurfurstendamm which is THE place to shop till you drop!Only a 2 minute walk to the S-Bahn and the U-bahn.Breakfast was plentiful and very good with choice of hot and cold buffet. Bar area was open until 2 am with an excepionally long happy hour!Reception staff couldn't have been more helpful, informing us of places to see and how to negotiate the underground system.Rooms were very clean and spacious as one would expect from German standards. 
